{
  "stem": "17.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like I said, they were this-- this Judenrat, probably, that organized this self-help, and also encouraged people, whoever it was, in a position to help others.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there were even-- there were sort of parties that people would gather together and collect money for the poor, collect money for especially sick family, or a sick child, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that was like a [INAUDIBLE] of a normal life, but was still livable.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I mentioned there were [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's-- that was-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they-- they-- they were teaching different trades.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I took the sewing and millinery course.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were teachers, dressmakers, that gave us the instruction.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so I was occupied with this, and then that was rather-- rather it made sense, let's say, and you thought that there would be a future.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And Henry was taking different jobs, I mean, working for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were-- I am calling job, but I-- that was slave labor, because that was never paid for.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A bowl of soup, or maybe some piece of meat or a little sugar.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that was the-- the-- the highest reward, what it was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But that was nothing on permanent basis.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "At times, he even started to-- to produce something that was like this little cooking utensil, like a small oven, which required very small amount of wood or coal, and it would heat up quickly, and you could cook on it quickly.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So that was a very good idea, but unfortunately, didn't last too long.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because again, there came a new changed border of the ghetto, and we had to leave everything and move to completely different quarters.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and then-- let me tell you some pictures from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
